dcterms:description: The KOSPI 200 index is a weighted combination of the 200 most traded securities in the Korean stock exchange. The dataset includes change ratios of the KOSPI 200 and various indexes such as currency, commodities, and global indexes, which are closely related to Korean financial markets.
dcterms:title: KOSPI 200
